cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image inpainting. The use of PixelCNNs suggests that it may also belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper may fall under the graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories due to its focus on image generation and manipulation.
